WEBVTT

00:06:28.787 --> 00:06:30.442
Cryptocurrencies are digital money

00:06:30.466 --> 00:06:33.334
that isn't run by any government or bank.

00:06:33.358 --> 00:06:37.419
It's money designed to work
in a world without intermediaries.

00:06:38.153 --> 00:06:41.186
Bitcoin is the most ubiquitous
cryptocurrency,

00:06:41.210 --> 00:06:42.907
but there are hundreds of them.

00:06:42.931 --> 00:06:46.408
There's Ethereum, Litecoin,
Stellar, Dogecoin,

00:06:46.432 --> 00:06:48.978
and those are just a few
of the more popular ones.

00:06:49.408 --> 00:06:52.009
And these things are real money.

00:06:52.507 --> 00:06:54.362
The sushi restaurant down my street

00:06:54.386 --> 00:06:55.541
takes Bitcoin.

00:06:55.966 --> 00:07:00.091
I have an app on my phone
that I can use to buy sashimi.